data.description: This stunning single story brick home is situated in a peaceful neighborhood nestled in a Cul-de sac. It has a great size back yard with a covered patio that is great for gatherings. It has a nice foyer as you walk into the home that leads into a spacious open floor plan the living room, dining area, and kitchen. With its high ceilings and large windows, it creates lots of space and allows beautiful light to illuminate rooms.  The kitchen showcases beautiful granite countertops, gorgeous back-splash and adjacent is the breakfast room with its own exit to the backyard. The floorplan was curated for privacy between master bedroom and other bedrooms. All flooring is ceramic title and owner installed hardwood floor in all bedrooms. Bedrooms are all spacious with ample closet space. The fourth bedroom would be used as an office since it open towards the living room with its beautiful French doors. Master bedroom offers ample space and an on-suite bathroom with a soak tub.
